  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Descriptive, prospective, multicenter evaluation of spleen injury treatment in the Languedoc
      Roussilon region according to trauma severity, morbi-mortality and length of hospitalization.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
